notes: The Hawaiian Electric Company Inc. (HECO), under requirements of National Pollutant Discharge Elimination System (NPDES) Permit HI0000019, Section C.5, annually conducts and reports results of a monitoring program for waters receiving effluent from the Kahe Generating Station, O'ahu, Hawai'i. This data set includes daily water discharge and unadjusted intake temperature data logs collected as part of this monitoring program from 1992 to 1997 (Appendix B in annual reports). These data are filed under NODC Accession # 9900021.
